Assemble a team of characters to find components for Iso-8.
Powered up Ravagers are attacking a S.T.R.I.K.E. facility! What's enhancing their power, and can Iron Man stop them?
Scientist Supreme believes this new element, Iso-8, will put A.I.M. back on top! If only she can get her hands on some...
Ultron's drones have beaten S.T.R.I.K.E. and Scientist Supreme to the cache of Iso-8!
Ultron himself has arrived to defend his freshly claimed Iso-8 from S.T.R.I.K.E. and Scientist Supreme.
Scientist Supreme shows Nick Fury her brand new Large Hadron Kaleidoscope when Ultron returns, looking for revenge.
Graviton attempts to secure an A.I.M. facility overrun with corrupted S.H.I.E.L.D. agents for Iso-8 storage.
The enemy is willing to bring the facility down around A.I.M. rather than lose and face Ultimus!
A secure warehouse in Canada is Graviton's next potential warehouse, but it's overrun by Mercenaries!
Pushing deeper into the facility, Graviton hopes to weed out any remaining Mercenaries.
Abandoning the Canadian facility, A.I.M. seeks to reclaim their final warehouse from a rouge splinter group of Hydra!
Looking to avoid the damage done in a firefight, Scientist Supreme hopes to drive Hydra out with an experimental toxin.
Secure in their new Iso-8 storage facility, A.I.M. and Scientist Supreme must face off against a powered-up Yondu!
Recycle Iso-8 to earn IONs. IONs are used to upgrade a character to the next tier of ISO-8.
Crafting Currency is used for crafting Iso-8 and buying components
